        <comment>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="0">Data was obtained from industries of Switzerland, Germany and Austria. certain exchanges are proxies (CH for RER), specially for the petrol consumption the proxy "operation, passenger car" has been used; data stem from Switzerland, Germany and Austria</text>
        </comment>
      </geography>
      <technology technologyLevel="3">
        <comment>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="0">This dataset corresponds to a mix of different brick production technologies (different firing fuels) in Austria, Germany and Switzerland.</text>
        </comment>
      </technology>
